Ta eller velg et bilde for å starte: Take or select a picture to get started
Artsorakelet kjenner ikke igjen menneske: Artsorakel does not recognize people, pets, garden plants, etc.
Artsorakelet er utviklet av Artsdatabank: Artsorakel is developed by the Norwegian Biodiversity Information Centre (Artsdatabanken) in collaboration with Naturalis Biodiversity Center. The app attempts to identify species in pictures using machine learning.
